### Ask Weather
POST http://localhost:9601/api/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What's the weather like in Seoul?"
}

###

### Weather with Unit
POST http://localhost:9601/api/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Tell me the weather in Busan in fahrenheit"
}

###

### Multiple Cities
POST http://localhost:9601/api/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Compare the weather between Seoul and Jeju"
}
